gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe9451564b421715662e65eb8d5dfc9f676bf7e","tid":447010,"uid":79404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:49:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.diypc.hk/archives/19085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.diypc.hk%2Farchives%2F19085&d=uBVAaNA4o%2FoePBNApAJECBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=c4208f4b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.diypc.hk/archives/19085</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50aeb97cc4e6e26ccf2150c33a09c2a695f9642c","tid":447010,"uid":73695,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:50:48.000Z","msg":"唔可以咁做<br />\n一張卡駁3-4個芒都冇問題，點解要一卡一芒？"},{"pid":"10c6edac68a5ce01d6ea8f4b33f1f8e6c974997e","tid":447010,"uid":10538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打算兩張卡駁兩個唔同MON。<br />\n<br />\n首先，咁樣組合有無咩大問題？，開GAME/程式係咪係邊個MON按出黎隻GAME就跟邊個顯卡config 同邊個mon解像度？ 駛唔駛點樣SET法？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">p.s. 宜家我用緊GTX560 (遲D會另外轉高階GTX)，目前想加多張顯示卡，應該一係1080ti 一係Vega(for free sync)<br />\n</span></blockquote><br />\n邏輯上無問題。技術上做唔到。"},{"pid":"776a35af6606b7feea50c4392c4433c1a214dd74","tid":447010,"uid":154436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:01:28.000Z","msg":"其實一張卡就可以出兩個MON或者以上。<br />\n<br />\n個WINDOW可以設一個主MON, 則是有WINDOW開始LOGO果頁, 到時打機就會個頁全頻。(桌面&gt;右鍵&gt;screen resolution)<br />\n<br />\n理論上, 唔睇牌子插得就用得, 好多人插左兩個卡做交易平台。<br />\n<br />\n但實際打機就未試過,"},{"pid":"68f33e39ac06c4c7e43f1e7dabd914679065cc24","tid":447010,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實一張卡就可以出兩個MON或者以上。<br />\n<br />\n個WINDOW可以設一個主MON, 則是有WINDOW開始LOGO果頁, 到時打機就會個頁全頻。(桌面&gt;右鍵&gt;screen resolution)<br />\n<br />\n理論上, 唔睇牌子插得就用得, 好多人插左兩個卡做交易平台。<br />\n<br />\n但實際打機就未試過,</blockquote><br />\n咁另外想問下,同一張卡,一個插dp 2k,一個插hdmi 1080p<br />\n<br />\n係電腦度較左做同時顯示,跟住2邊個解像度都變左好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n之前仲係1080p+1080p果陣好正常,mon換左做2k後就唔得了<br />\n<br />\n咁係正常定係有d咩要set?"},{"pid":"8711d9acf1d9e84311c6a15454f49bb5f809cc85","tid":447010,"uid":78554,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"樓上咁多位柒曬其實係做到 連同時CF+SLI都得<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YqkI7bOfRkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYqkI7bOfRkA&d=uBVAaNA4o%2FoePBNApAJECBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9320b228\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YqkI7bOfRkA</a><br />\n<br />\n所以樓主可以自己google下點樣SETUP <br />\n不過依D咁奇怪嘅SETUP要搞幾耐同出黎效果係點就唔知"},{"pid":"19412c83be0e0707d631d91447aa187564a97492","tid":447010,"uid":119696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔可以咁做<br />\n一張卡駁3-4個芒都冇問題，點解要一卡一芒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一部mon有f-sync 一部無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3187b213b5e87cd187da04049cfb066e8e4027","tid":447010,"uid":119696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實一張卡就可以出兩個MON或者以上。<br />\n<br />\n個WINDOW可以設一個主MON, 則是有WINDOW開始LOGO果頁, 到時打機就會個頁全頻。(桌面&gt;右鍵&gt;screen resolution)<br />\n<br />\n理論上, 唔睇牌子插得就用得, 好多人插左兩個卡做交易平台。<br />\n<br />\n但實際打機就未試過,</blockquote><br />\n咁另外想問下,同一張卡,一個插dp 2k,一個插hdmi 1080p<br />\n<br />\n係電腦度較左做同時顯示,跟住2邊個解像度都變左好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n之前仲係1080p+1080p果陣好正常,mon換左做2k後就唔得了<br />\n<br />\n咁係正常定係有d咩要set?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問呀爸打，我正正就構思緊一部4K mon，一部gaming mon一齊行dual monitors, 插一張卡架話點樣可以做到一邊出4k, 一邊出返1080p <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e80ec36e39820ed9244b952699987f6f511b8e","tid":447010,"uid":119696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上咁多位柒曬其實係做到 連同時CF+SLI都得<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YqkI7bOfRkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYqkI7bOfRkA&d=uBVAaNA4o%2FoePBNApAJECBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9320b228\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YqkI7bOfRkA</a><br />\n<br />\n所以樓主可以自己google下點樣SETUP <br />\n不過依D咁奇怪嘅SETUP要搞幾耐同出黎效果係點就唔知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪難SET到仆街？<br />\n新手係咪唔好咁樣搞會好D?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae561802263d9b70dc78b56f175175671f2a7820","tid":447010,"uid":151490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f646032f8b92bf4981246f362cfdf19efc5ffffc","tid":447010,"uid":140707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問如果個顯示卡有2個hdmi就咁插哂佢就可以出到2個mon獨立畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗唔洗set d咩   求巴打解答</blockquote><br />\n桌面&gt;右鍵&gt;display setting&gt;Multiple displays&gt; Extend these displays"},{"pid":"9bdcdbe81bf2fb4ddc006538f7dfb3fcbef7eafa","tid":447010,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓上咁多位柒曬其實係做到 連同時CF+SLI都得<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YqkI7bOfRkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYqkI7bOfRkA&d=uBVAaNA4o%2FoePBNApAJECBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9320b228\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YqkI7bOfRkA</a><br />\n<br />\n所以樓主可以自己google下點樣SETUP <br />\n不過依D咁奇怪嘅SETUP要搞幾耐同出黎效果係點就唔知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪難SET到仆街？<br />\n新手係咪唔好咁樣搞會好D?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難SET我唔知, 但新手就絕對唔建議你做<br />\n用起上黎一定會有好多奇難雜症<br />\n你自己唔識diagnose 死硬<br />\n<br />\n另一方面我想問下點解你想咁SETUP?"},{"pid":"c5c162f2e64d2de43572ef1e1bbbf329e222b575","tid":447010,"uid":154436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實一張卡就可以出兩個MON或者以上。<br />\n<br />\n個WINDOW可以設一個主MON, 則是有WINDOW開始LOGO果頁, 到時打機就會個頁全頻。(桌面&gt;右鍵&gt;screen resolution)<br />\n<br />\n理論上, 唔睇牌子插得就用得, 好多人插左兩個卡做交易平台。<br />\n<br />\n但實際打機就未試過,</blockquote><br />\n咁另外想問下,同一張卡,一個插dp 2k,一個插hdmi 1080p<br />\n<br />\n係電腦度較左做同時顯示,跟住2邊個解像度都變左好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n之前仲係1080p+1080p果陣好正常,mon換左做2k後就唔得了<br />\n<br />\n咁係正常定係有d咩要set?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問呀爸打，我正正就構思緊一部4K mon，一部gaming mon一齊行dual monitors, 插一張卡架話點樣可以做到一邊出4k, 一邊出返1080p <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n桌面&gt;右鍵&gt;screen resolution 可以設4K OR 1080p, 兩個MON都可以獨單設定。<br />\n<br />\n如果同時顯示, 其實中一個解像度唔正常, 你可以交換線睇下係MON出問題定個設定出問題..<br />\n<br />\n利申: 老子都未買過1080嫁, GOOGLE加幻想, 你也做得到。"},{"pid":"c45e8763b3857a13ddd6704d952594e5e4bd8dd1","tid":447010,"uid":140707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實一張卡就可以出兩個MON或者以上。<br />\n<br />\n個WINDOW可以設一個主MON, 則是有WINDOW開始LOGO果頁, 到時打機就會個頁全頻。(桌面&gt;右鍵&gt;screen resolution)<br />\n<br />\n理論上, 唔睇牌子插得就用得, 好多人插左兩個卡做交易平台。<br />\n<br />\n但實際打機就未試過,</blockquote><br />\n咁另外想問下,同一張卡,一個插dp 2k,一個插hdmi 1080p<br />\n<br />\n係電腦度較左做同時顯示,跟住2邊個解像度都變左好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n之前仲係1080p+1080p果陣好正常,mon換左做2k後就唔得了<br />\n<br />\n咁係正常定係有d咩要set?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問呀爸打，我正正就構思緊一部4K mon，一部gaming mon一齊行dual monitors, 插一張卡架話點樣可以做